-- Ejercicio 1
nombresDeUsuarios :: RedSocial -> [String]
nombresDeUsuarios red = map nombreDeUsuario (usuarios red)

-- Ejercicio 2
amigosDe :: RedSocial -> Usuario -> [Usuario]
amigosDe red u = [v | (u', v) <- relaciones red, u' == u] ++ [u' | (u', v) <- relaciones red, v == u]

-- Ejercicio 3
cantidadDeAmigos :: RedSocial -> Usuario -> Int
cantidadDeAmigos red u = length (amigosDe red u)

-- Ejercicio 4
usuarioConMasAmigos :: RedSocial -> Usuario
usuarioConMasAmigos red = maximumBy (comparing (cantidadDeAmigos red)) (usuarios red)

-- Ejercicio 5
estaRobertoCarlos :: RedSocial -> Bool
estaRobertoCarlos red = any (\u -> cantidadDeAmigos red u > 1000000) (usuarios red)

-- Ejercicio 6
publicacionesDe :: RedSocial -> Usuario -> [Publicacion]
publicacionesDe red u = filter (\pub -> usuarioDePublicacion pub == u) (publicaciones red)

-- Ejercicio 7
publicacionesQueLeGustanA :: RedSocial -> Usuario -> [Publicacion]
publicacionesQueLeGustanA red u = filter (\pub -> u `elem` likesDePublicacion pub) (publicaciones red)

-- Ejercicio 8
lesGustanLasMismasPublicaciones :: RedSocial -> Usuario -> Usuario -> Bool
lesGustanLasMismasPublicaciones red u1 u2 = publicacionesQueLeGustanA red u1 == publicacionesQueLeGustanA red u2

-- Ejercicio 9
tieneUnSeguidorFiel :: RedSocial -> Usuario -> Bool
tieneUnSeguidorFiel red u = any (\u2 -> u /= u2 && all (\pub -> u2 `elem` likesDePublicacion pub) (publicacionesDe red u)) (usuarios red)

-- Ejercicio 10
existeSecuenciaDeAmigos :: RedSocial -> Usuario -> Usuario -> Bool
existeSecuenciaDeAmigos red u1 u2 = existeCamino (relaciones red) u1 u2
  where
    existeCamino :: [Relacion] -> Usuario -> Usuario -> Bool
    existeCamino _ u1 u2 | u1 == u2 = True
    existeCamino rels u1 u2 = any (\v -> existeCamino (delete (u1, v) rels) v u2) (amigosDe red u1)

define startGame()
set progress to 0
repeat until segments collected = total segments
  wait for segment to be collected
  if segment is blue then
    add [1] to progress
  else if segment is orange then
    change progress by [-1]
  else if segment is light blue then
    add (progress * 2) to progress
  else if segment is pink then
    change progress by [-10]
  else if segment is red then
    play sound [BSOD]
    go to x: (random position), y: (random position)
    wait for [any] key press
    startGame()
  else if segment is gray then
    do nothing
  else if segment is green then
    set progress to [100]
  end
end

fight :: EnemyArmy -> Army -> Army
fight [] army = army -- No enemies, allies win unharmed
fight enemies [] = [] -- No allies, return empty list
fight (enemy:enemies) allies = case enemy of
    M (Alive mage@(Master _ _ spell)) -> fight enemies (map (applyDamage spell) allies)
    _ -> fight enemies allies -- If it's not a mage, move to the next unit

applyDamage :: Spell -> Unit -> Unit
applyDamage spell (E (Alive (Golem h))) = E (Alive (Golem (max 0 (spell h))))
applyDamage spell (E (Alive (HaskellElemental h))) = E (Alive (HaskellElemental (max 0 (spell h))))
applyDamage _ unit = unit -- If it's Dead or a Mage, we don't apply the spell

        o.currency,
        SUM(o.amount) as amount,
        SUM(o.price) as total_price
    FROM "Order" o
		JOIN "Pack" p ON p.id = o."packId"
		JOIN "Collection" c ON c.id = p."collectionId"
    WHERE o.status IS TRUE
    GROUP BY updated_date, o.currency, c.name ->> c."defaultLang"
    ORDER BY updated_date DESC
